headline: Government Copper Stockpiles Put Freeport McMoRan Valuation And Role In Focus
summary: US Project Vault and parallel Chinese efforts are expanding government-backed copper stockpiles. These programs are increasing attention on long term copper supply security and logistics. As a major producer, Freeport-McMoRan (NYSE:FCX) sits at the center of discussions about government driven copper demand. For you as an investor, the growing US and Chinese copper stockpiling programs highlight how central Freeport-McMoRan is to the physical copper market. The company focuses on copper...
